ith tourists, restaurants playing live music which makes it more vibrant and lively when the sun goes down. Head to the popular pubs here famous for offering delectable beverages. Tito&#8217;s Pub in Calangute is a must-visit for both local and international tourists to enjoy the nightlife of Goa.<\/p>\n<p>To reach this destination, one can book a cab from Panaji or Margao. Also, there are rentals bikes and car available that offer well-maintained rides to take you to this famous tourist destination in Goa.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Calangute is a town in the coastal line of North Goa and is centrally located between Candolim and Baga. Located just 15 kilometres away from Goa&#8217;s capital city Panjim, Calangute is an incredible beach destination for both Indian and foreign tourist. Popularly known as the &#8220;Queen of Beaches&#8221; in Goa, it offers long, sandy Calangute [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":200,"template":"","meta":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/location\/202"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/location"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/location"}],"version-history":[{"count":11,"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/location\/202\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":432,"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/location\/202\/revisions\/432"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/200"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/amorgroupofhotels.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=202"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}